      "originalText": "THE SIDECAR TRICK (most common junior mistake)\nGateway sends to Pod IP → iptables intercepts → Sidecar (Envoy) → localhost loopback → App\nSame host · Same network namespace · 0 extra physical hops · tiny CPU cost only",
